---
// How It Works section - Simple 3-step flow
---

<section class="how-it-works section" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header reveal">
      <span class="label label-coral">How It Works</span>
      <h2>Start building real habits in 3 steps</h2>
      <p>Simple setup. Powerful accountability. Results that last.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="steps-container">
      <div class="steps-line" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="steps-grid">
        <div class="step reveal">
          <div class="step-number">1</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Create a micro-commitment</h3>
            <p>Pick something so small you can't say no. 10 pushups. 5 minutes reading. One glass of water. Set a time-box: 7, 14, 21, or 30 days.</p>
            <div class="step-example">
              <span class="example-emoji">10</span>
              <span class="example-text">pushups before 9am</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step reveal">
          <div class="step-number">2</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Add accountability</h3>
            <p>Invite a partner or create a group. Enable "All Accountable" mode so everyone's streak depends on everyone checking in.</p>
            <div class="step-avatars">
              <div class="step-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FF6B5A, #FF8F7A);">Y</div>
              <div class="step-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #57C760, #7BD982);">M</div>
              <div class="step-avatar" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #9466DE, #A880E8);">S</div>
              <span class="step-avatar-text">Your accountability team</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="step reveal">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Check in daily</h3>
            <p>Tap to log your completion. Optional photo proof with watermarks. Build your streak. Your partner gets notified when you complete.</p>
            <div class="step-checkin">
              <div class="checkin-btn">
                <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3">
                  <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"></polyline>
                </svg>
                Done
              </div>
              <span class="checkin-time">Takes 5 seconds</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Feature highlight -->
    <div class="works-highlight reveal">
      <div class="highlight-card">
        <div class="highlight-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-content">
          <h4>Time-boxed commitments</h4>
          <p>7, 14, 21, or 30 days. Finite feels achievable. Renew if you want to continue.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-card">
        <div class="highlight-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"></path>
            <path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-content">
          <h4>Smart nudges</h4>
          <p>Get reminded when your partner completes. Notifications timed to your preferred time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-card">
        <div class="highlight-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 15s1-1 4-1 5 2 8 2 4-1 4-1V3s-1 1-4 1-5-2-8-2-4 1-4 1z"></path>
            <line x1="4" y1="22" x2="4" y2="15"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-content">
          <h4>Streak protection</h4>
          <p>Pause for illness or travel. 4-hour grace period after midnight. Life happens.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    background: var(--bg-primary);
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin: var(--space-4) 0;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .steps-container {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  }

  .steps-line {
    position: absolute;
    top: 45px;
    left: 15%;
    right: 15%;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--coral), var(--purple), var(--green));
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .steps-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-8);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .step {
    text-align: center;
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .step:hover {
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2xl);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 72px;
    height: 72px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--coral), var(--coral-light));
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-extrabold);
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-6);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-coral);
  }

  .step:nth-child(2) .step-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--purple), var(--purple-light));
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(148, 102, 222, 0.35);
  }

  .step:nth-child(3) .step-number {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-light));
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.35);
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .step-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-5);
  }

  /* Step 1 example */
  .step-example {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    background: var(--gray-50);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
  }

  .example-emoji {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .example-text {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* Step 2 avatars */
  .step-avatars {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .step-avatar {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: var(--white);
    font-weight: var(--font-bold);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    margin-left: -8px;
    border: 3px solid var(--white);
  }

  .step-avatar:first-child {
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .step-avatar-text {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
  }

  /* Step 3 check-in */
  .step-checkin {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
  }

  .checkin-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--green), var(--green-light));
    color: var(--white);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(87, 199, 96, 0.35);
  }

  .checkin-time {
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Highlight cards */
  .works-highlight {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .highlight-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-4);
    padding: var(--space-6);
    background: var(--gray-50);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    transition: all var(--transition-slow);
  }

  .highlight-card:hover {
    background: var(--white);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .highlight-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.1), rgba(255, 107, 90, 0.05));
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .highlight-content h4 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--font-semibold);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .highlight-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .steps-line {
      display: none;
    }

    .steps-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .works-highlight {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .step {
      padding: var(--space-6);
    }

    .step-number {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
    }
  }
</style>
